  "commentary": "With SPX at 6924 sitting between the flip (6858) and max positive gamma wall (6950), dealers are currently long gamma and will sell into strength as we approach the 6950 resistance level where they hold maximum hedging flow. The thick positive GEX concentration from 6900-7000 creates a strong magnet effect that should cap upside momentum and encourage mean reversion back toward this range. Watch 6950 as the critical dealer selling zone - any push above likely faces heavy resistance, while a break below 6900 opens up downside toward the flip at 6858.\n\nBottom line: expect the market to get sticky and choppy between 6900-6950 as dealers defend these levels.",
